    "description": "&quot;<i>你既不是士兵也不是战士，只是一名陷入奇怪事件中的普通维修工。但你必须战斗，被迫逃亡。最重要的是，你必须帮助飞船上处于冷冻状态的船员在茫茫太空中活下去。只有你能拯救他们的性命，或防止他们被永久冷冻。你违背自己的意愿成为了英雄。你需要指挥他人，也需要痛下杀手。</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >只有小心谨慎、反应迅速的人才能幸存</h2>一艘巨大的星舰在外太空航行，远离所有行星、飞船和天体。处于冷冻状态的未来移民、工人、士兵……还有其他生物在甲板上等着你。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要亮点：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>探索飞船残骸，寻找物资并帮助其他幸存者<br></li><li>解开谜题，躲避陷阱<br></li><li>用各种方式打败怪异的外星生物<br></li><li>将倒霉的船员解冻，他们或许能帮你解开谜团</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><br><strong>探索和资源</strong><br>雄伟壮丽的宇宙飞船变成了危险的残骸，它现在看起来更像一座坟墓，而不是载满未来移民的太空船。你必须仔细调查“统治”号的不同部分，寻找线索和资源。当然，最重要的是氧气——如果失去氧气，你将在几分钟内死亡。电池也十分有用，你需要用它们点亮手电筒。当电池快耗尽时，手电筒会开始闪烁，然后你将陷入无尽的黑暗……<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460010/extras/f431ce0b0e54411e4e94936134a9100a.poster.avif?t=1754055541\" width=600 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460010/extras/f431ce0b0e54411e4e94936134a9100a.webm?t=1754055541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460010/extras/f431ce0b0e54411e4e94936134a9100a.mp4?t=1754055541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>引人入胜的剧情</strong><br>显然，你目前最重要的任务是活下去。但要活下去，你必须解开一个谜团——这艘本该将移民送往遥远世界的宇宙飞船究竟发生了什么？船员们都怎么样了？ <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460010/extras/54de2e2c3e8a95174f0fbe4d37a71470.poster.avif?t=1754055541\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460010/extras/54de2e2c3e8a95174f0fbe4d37a71470.webm?t=1754055541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460010/extras/54de2e2c3e8a95174f0fbe4d37a71470.mp4?t=1754055541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>这些在飞船残骸里游荡的奇怪生物是什么？你到底身在何方，在太空的什么方位？<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460010/extras/310b032001d300b20f983fa22f923154.poster.avif?t=1754055541\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460010/extras/310b032001d300b20f983fa22f923154.webm?t=1754055541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460010/extras/310b032001d300b20f983fa22f923154.mp4?t=1754055541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>不同的生存策略</strong><br>飞船残骸上到处都是怪异丑陋的生物。它们有些行动迟缓，有些头脑愚钝，有些反应迅速，有些敏锐狡黠，还有一些全副武装（仅举几个例子）。你可以通过射击、地雷或临时陷阱消灭其中一部分。但大多数时候，你必须运用智慧，隐匿身形，并祈祷运气来避开这些生物或是逃脱它们的追踪。你需要随时注意自己拥有的氧气量——缺氧会导致死亡……<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460010/extras/0c18b1e26793a7b78c003f36b4073c9d.poster.avif?t=1754055541\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460010/extras/0c18b1e26793a7b78c003f36b4073c9d.webm?t=1754055541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460010/extras/0c18b1e26793a7b78c003f36b4073c9d.mp4?t=1754055541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>但最好的办法是逃跑！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460010/extras/36c43a292911ac0bdc06d985e6101c57.poster.avif?t=1754055541\" width=600 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460010/extras/36c43a292911ac0bdc06d985e6101c57.webm?t=1754055541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460010/extras/36c43a292911ac0bdc06d985e6101c57.mp4?t=1754055541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>其他的可怜人</strong><br>幸运的是，这艘在太空漂浮的失事飞船上还有其他的可怜人。而你——普通的维修工——可以利用他们。你可以唤醒一些人，他们会根据自己的能力，尽其所能帮助你。其他人将继续沉睡，等待境况好转的那一天。记住，你的同伴也需要氧气，而三个人消耗的氧气量可比一个人多得多……因此，你必须做出评估，衡量他们能为你提供的帮助是否比消耗的氧气更有价值？<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460010/extras/98a555e29a9b706144a909bc727e8796.poster.avif?t=1754055541\" width=600 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460010/extras/98a555e29a9b706144a909bc727e8796.webm?t=1754055541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460010/extras/98a555e29a9b706144a909bc727e8796.mp4?t=1754055541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i><strong>记住：在飞船上，你的敌人能听到你的尖叫……</strong></i>&quot;",
